general.desc: Nova MSC Bhd is an investment holding company. The company is engaged in software research and development and the provision of e-business solutions through the sale of application software and professional services for software customization and implementation. Its Geographical segments include Malaysia and Singapore. The products of the company include Pavo, which is an e-Government software that facilities the online submission of application documents; Avicenna, which is a fully integrated cloud-based system that takes care of the administrative needs, EyScan, a cloud-based platform that manages and executes SELENA+, system that performs automated retinal photo analysis and others.
